<!-- ═══ S8 KPI FRAMEWORK ═══ -->
<div class="slide cs" id="s8">
  <div class="sh"><h2>The KPI Framework — Four Numbers, One Decision Tree</h2><span class="st">Section 02 — KPIs</span></div>
  <div class="sb">
    <div class="g4" style="flex-shrink:0;">
      <div class="metric"><div class="m-label">Hook Rate Target</div><div class="m-val">25%+</div><div class="m-desc">3-sec views ÷ impressions. Below 15% = Andromeda deprioritizes before auction.</div></div>
      <div class="metric orange"><div class="m-label">Hold Rate Target</div><div class="m-val">20%+</div><div class="m-desc">30-sec views ÷ impressions. Below 10% = script/body problem, not hook.</div></div>
      <div class="metric green"><div class="m-label">Cost Per Qualified Call</div><div class="m-val">⅓ CAC</div><div class="m-desc">$4,500 offer → $1,125 max CAC → $375 max per qualified call</div></div>
      <div class="metric"><div class="m-label">CAC Maximum</div><div class="m-val">25%</div><div class="m-desc">Of offer price. $4,500 offer = $1,125 max. Gives you 4x ROAS floor.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1;overflow:hidden;">
      <table class="dt">
        <thead><tr><th>KPI</th><th>Target</th><th>What It Diagnoses</th><th>When to Act</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><strong>Hook Rate</strong></td><td><span class="badge bo">25%+</span></td><td>Does your first 3 seconds stop the scroll? Andromeda's #1 gatekeeper signal.</td><td>Below 15%: kill or swap hook only. Body may be fine.</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Hold Rate (30s)</strong></td><td><span class="badge bo">20%+</span></td><td>Does your message hold attention after the hook? Script/pacing problem.</td><td>Below 10%: add re-hook at 10-12s. Move CTA to 30-45s.</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Cost/Qualified Call</strong></td><td><span class="badge bg">⅓ of CAC</span></td><td>Is your funnel converting traffic to calls? Fastest decision signal available.</td><td>2x target: audit funnel + creative before adding budget.</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>CAC</strong></td><td><span class="badge bg">Max 25% offer</span></td><td>Is your ad system profitable? Slowest to confirm — takes weeks.</td><td>Above 30%: structural problem, not just creative.</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Lead to Book Rate</strong></td><td><span class="badge bn">3–5% DM</span></td><td>Are DM leads converting to calls? Below 3% = messaging or follow-up problem.</td><td>Below 3%: DM script or qualification issue, not the ad.</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <div class="callout"><p><strong>Jordan's rule:</strong> Cost per qualified call is the only KPI you can make fast decisions from as a coach. ROAS takes weeks to confirm. Hook rate and qualified call cost tell you within 48 hours whether an ad is worth keeping.</p></div>
