<div class="slide cs" id="s17">
  <div class="sh"><h2>The Four Variation Types — What Creates a New Entity vs. What Doesn't</h2><span class="st">Section 04 — Winning Variations</span></div>
  <div class="sb">
    <div style="flex:1;overflow:hidden;">
